Package chav1961.funnypro

This package contains all the classes to support SPI protocol for javax.script package incorporation, and a Stand-alone application class to make soncole-oriented application

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    This class implements stand-alone console-oriented application for the Funny Prolog interpreter
    FunnyProEngine
    This class implements engine for the Funny prolog interpreter.
    FunnyProEngineFactory
    This class implements engine factory for the Funny Prolog interpreter.
